Blood Moon Diana is not redundant because the thematic is not at all relevant to Diana. Cho'Gath is a void creature, so there is no Void Cho. Blitzcrank is a robot, so you can't make a robot a robot; And Darius is already Noxian.

Diana is not a mask wearing Asia-inspired entity based on the oni and spirits of ancient Japan. Diana is based on ancient Greco-Roman warrior. The Blood Moon design, being largely inspired by Japan and featuring reds and blacks along with the iconic masks, is not a duplication of any design of hers.

